elements.name: Booking hotels with adactin web portal

steps.name: user is on the adatctin page
user should login with valid "vinodelango" and "kingmaker"
user should search hotels "Melbourne","Hotel Sunshine","Double","1 - One","05/12/2021","06/12/2021","1 - One","1 - One" and click search
user should select the hotel and click continue
user shoud enter the "vinod","elangovan","madambakkam","4616800006561245","VISA","February""2022","245"and should click booknow
user should print the generated orderid
